  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the grill to medium-high heat",
    "In a large bowl, whisk together olive oil, lemon juice, garlic, sumac, salt, and black pepper",
    "Add the pork tenderloin pieces to the bowl and toss to coat",
    "Thread the pork pieces onto skewers",
    "Grill the kebabs for 10-12 minutes, turning occasionally",
    "Garnish with parsley and serve hot",
    "Let the kebabs rest for 5 minutes before serving"
